      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I spent three years in Washington, then became a partner in a Chicago firm that represented Sears Roebuck, Whirlpool corporation, a number of-- I actually incorporated Sears Roebuck.",
      "word_count": 28
